despite the wonderful stuff

00:45:05.970 --> 00:45:11.700
that you see from
Curry and Thompson.

00:45:11.700 --> 00:45:12.857
It just didn't work.

00:45:12.857 --> 00:45:13.690
AUDIENCE: Thank you.

00:45:13.690 --> 00:45:14.180
I'll keep that in mind.

00:45:14.180 --> 00:45:14.910
KAREEM ABDUL-JABBAR:
