00:46:51.790 --> 00:46:54.200
But then, if you start
creating a problem,

00:46:54.200 --> 00:46:56.690
you're going to get a lot
of negative attention.

00:46:56.690 --> 00:46:58.450
And that's what happened.

00:46:58.450 --> 00:47:01.297
I think for the
Muslim community,

00:47:01.297 --> 00:47:02.630
they're going to have to engage.

00:47:02.630 --> 00:47:04.213
They're going to
have to do everything

00:47:04.213 --> 00:47:07.900
they can to show Americans
that they are just

00:47:07.900 --> 00:47:11.710
as happy to be here as
all the other Americans.

00:47:11.710 --> 00:47:13.920
Most Muslims are really
happy to be here,

00:47:13.920 --> 00:47:16.040
because if they were
over in the Middle East,

00:47:16.040 --> 00:47:18.560
or wherever that their
families came from,

00:47:18.560 --> 00:47:21.540
